<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 00:59:09 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>日本媒体称，日本海军驱逐舰进入中国台湾附近海域，引发北京担忧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japan-navy-destroyer-enters-china-waters-near-taiwan-sparking-beijing-concerns-2024-07-11/</link><description>日本媒体周三晚间报道称，本月早些时候，一艘日本海军驱逐舰在没有通知中国的情况下罕见地进入台湾附近的中国领海，引发了北京的“严重关切”。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 00:28:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japan-navy-destroyer-enters-china-waters-near-taiwan-sparking-beijing-concerns-2024-07-11/</guid></item><item><title>中国官方媒体称多个澳门政府网站遭到黑客攻击</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/several-macau-government-websites-hacked-says-chinese-state-media-2024-07-11/</link><description>据中国官方媒体周三晚间报道，澳门多个政府网站遭到黑客攻击，警方已展开刑事调查，追查犯罪根源。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 00:14:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/several-macau-government-websites-hacked-says-chinese-state-media-2024-07-11/</guid></item><item><title>北约峰会：华盛顿宣言的要点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/key-points-natos-washington-summit-declaration-2024-07-10/</link><description>北约国家领导人周三在华盛顿举行的峰会上发表声明，强调了对乌克兰的加入承诺，并对中国对俄罗斯的支持采取了更强硬的立场。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/key-points-natos-washington-summit-declaration-2024-07-10/</guid></item><item><title>美国财政部官员表示，美国需要针对中国产能过剩采取更强有力的防御措施</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us-needs-stronger-defenses-against-chinas-overcapacity-treasury-official-says-2024-07-10/</link><description>美国财政部最高经济外交官周三表示，美国可能需要在关税之外采取进一步“更有创意”的行动，以保护美国工业和工人免受中国日益过剩的工业产能的影响。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 20:07:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us-needs-stronger-defenses-against-chinas-overcapacity-treasury-official-says-2024-07-10/</guid></item><item><title>持不同政见者还是欺诈？流亡中国商人郭先生的审判即将结束</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/exiled-chinese-businessman-stole-millions-followers-us-prosecutor-says-2024-07-10/</link><description>郭文贵的欺诈案审判于周三接近尾声，一名检察官告诉陪审员，这位流亡的中国商人欺骗他的追随者，提供他在奢侈品上花费的数百万美元，而一名辩护律师称郭文贵是对中国共产党政府的误解批评者。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 18:53:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/legal/exiled-chinese-businessman-stole-millions-followers-us-prosecutor-says-2024-07-10/</guid></item><item><title>支付问题阻碍了俄罗斯对中国汽车的进口</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/payment-problems-stifle-russian-imports-chinese-cars-2024-07-10/</link><description>俄罗斯汽车经销商协会负责人告诉路透社，美国制裁造成的俄罗斯和中国之间的支付问题给过去两年供应国内市场的俄罗斯进口中国汽车带来了严重问题。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 15:18:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/payment-problems-stifle-russian-imports-chinese-cars-2024-07-10/</guid></item><item><title>由于对中国制造的电动汽车征收关税，特斯拉提高了欧洲 Model 3 的价格</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-raises-model-3-prices-germany-due-european-tariffs-china-made-evs-2024-07-10/</link><description>美国汽车制造商特斯拉周三表示，在欧盟对中国制造的电动汽车征收关税后，特斯拉已将其在德国、荷兰和西班牙等欧洲国家的 Model 3 汽车价格提高约 1,500 欧元（1,622 美元）。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 15:11:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-raises-model-3-prices-germany-due-european-tariffs-china-made-evs-2024-07-10/</guid></item><item><title>公报草案称北约抨击中国对俄罗斯的支持，支持乌克兰全面一体化</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/nato-slams-china-over-russia-support-backs-full-integration-ukraine-draft-2024-07-10/</link><description>路透社周三看到的一份联合公报草案显示，北约盟国将承诺支持乌克兰走上“不可逆转的一体化道路”，并呼吁中国停止对俄罗斯对基辅发动战争的一切支持。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 15:09:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/nato-slams-china-over-russia-support-backs-full-integration-ukraine-draft-2024-07-10/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，德国达成协议，削减华为在 5G 无线网络中的角色</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/germany-deal-cut-huaweis-role-5g-wireless-network-report-says-2024-07-10/</link><description>两位知情人士周三对路透社表示，德国政府和移动运营商已原则上同意在未来五年内逐步将中国科技公司的组件排除在德国 5G 无线网络之外。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 13:33:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/germany-deal-cut-huaweis-role-5g-wireless-network-report-says-2024-07-10/</guid></item><item><title>美国和墨西哥采取行动阻止中国规避关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/us-mexico-move-thwart-china-circumvention-us-steel-aluminum-tariffs-2024-07-10/</link><description>美国和墨西哥周三宣布了新措施，以实施北美“熔化和浇注”钢铁标准，打击中国和其他通过墨西哥运输产品的国家规避美国钢铁和铝关税的行为。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 13:21:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/us-mexico-move-thwart-china-circumvention-us-steel-aluminum-tariffs-2024-07-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国称印度无权开发有争议的边境地区</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/china-says-india-has-no-right-carry-out-development-arunachal-pradesh-2024-07-10/</link><description>中国外交部周三在回应路透社关于新德里计划在边境国家加快水电项目的报道时表示，印度无权在中国所说的藏南地区进行开发。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 11:59:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/china-says-india-has-no-right-carry-out-development-arunachal-pradesh-2024-07-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国与巴西试行牛肉追溯计划</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/land-use-biodiversity/china-brazil-try-out-beef-traceability-plan-2024-07-10/</link><description>官方媒体周三表示，全球最大的牛肉进口国中国和最大的牛肉供应国巴西将设立一项试点计划，作为使牛肉生产更加可持续的努力的一部分。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 11:00:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/land-use-biodiversity/china-brazil-try-out-beef-traceability-plan-2024-07-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国宣布更多卖空限制以稳定股市</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinese-regulator-suspend-securities-relending-curb-short-selling-2024-07-10/</link><description>中国证券监管机构周三宣布对卖空采取更多限制，并承诺对计算机驱动的程序交易进行更严格的审查，这是提振低迷股市的最新举措。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 10:48:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinese-regulator-suspend-securities-relending-curb-short-selling-2024-07-10/</guid></item><item><title>北京关注沙特主权财富基金的更多投资</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/beijing-eyes-more-investments-saudi-sovereign-wealth-fund-2024-07-10/</link><description>官方媒体周三称，北京市市长已告诉沙特阿拉伯主权财富基金总裁，希望该基金进一步扩大在中国首都的业务。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 10:27:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/beijing-eyes-more-investments-saudi-sovereign-wealth-fund-2024-07-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国称黄岩岛水域“非常好”，驳回菲律宾的担忧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-says-scarborough-shoal-waters-excellent-dismisses-philippine-concerns-2024-07-10/</link><description>就在菲律宾指责中国渔民破坏海洋环境几个月后，中国关于黄岩岛争议渔场周围海域的一份报告认为该海域水质优良，珊瑚礁健康。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 09:34:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-says-scarborough-shoal-waters-excellent-dismisses-philippine-concerns-2024-07-10/</guid></item></channel></rss>